[{"url_token": "hou-bao-shan-86", "headline": "且慢 前面听说风很大", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4715349669", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "4715349669", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "作为一个威海人来说的话。威海的海边其实都可以去看看，海水浴场的沙子比较细石头也少，建议外地游客去海水浴场洗海澡。那香海的海滩去看看就好，不建议下海。养马岛的海水十分清澈，就我在海边住了二十多年，第一次看见养马岛的海，我都有点不敢相信。太清了", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Barnett-Hou", "author_id": "2e8a273c2572d18c1677a5195cf3ea91", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "hou-bao-shan-86", "headline": "且慢 前面听说风很大", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4716779042", "reply_comment_id": "4715991702", "reply_root_comment_id": "4715349669", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "海水浴场要满足几个点，大概就是沙子的柔软度、石头的密度、海水的平缓度（就是有没有暗流或者威胁人类生命健康的生物等等等等），国际海水浴场是威海唯一一个国家认可的海水浴场，各种设备设施以及海滩海水都很完备。那香海只是区市弄的海水浴场，各方面还不是很完善。所以建议不要下海，毕竟有危险的概率比国际海水浴场多不少。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Barnett-Hou", "author_id": "2e8a273c2572d18c1677a5195cf3ea91", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "hou-bao-shan-86", "headline": "且慢 前面听说风很大", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4716546657", "reply_comment_id": "4716456994", "reply_root_comment_id": "4715349669", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "因为开发的晚，再加上这两三年才开始开放海滩，所以海水相比能清澈一点，但是建议想看清澈的海水还是去养马岛，那才是真清。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Barnett-Hou", "author_id": "2e8a273c2572d18c1677a5195cf3ea91", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhao-ran-21-63", "headline": "好好活着", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4716456994", "reply_comment_id": "4716779042", "reply_root_comment_id": "4715349669", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "嗯，现在还不太完善，不过海水是真的清澈，海边走一走拍拍照还是可以的。谢谢你的建议～", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "葡萄藤", "author_id": "65cc5ae04f9d1283943056a7323e4329", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhao-ran-21-63", "headline": "好好活着", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4715991702", "reply_comment_id": "4715349669", "reply_root_comment_id": "4715349669", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "那香海为什么不建议下海呢？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "葡萄藤", "author_id": "65cc5ae04f9d1283943056a7323e4329", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "zhang-xiao-ming-84-92", "headline": "努力幸福着~~", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4716167750", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "4716167750", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "请问养马岛建议去哪个景点呀？听说分前海和后海", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "路人甲", "author_id": "2e5313a07cb0ac6c56cd83ea9b07ade8", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}]